and the space to learn, to grow,

01:02:11.637 --> 01:02:15.000
to experience both life and death,

01:02:16.101 --> 01:02:17.882
to accomplish something worthwhile,

01:02:18.936 --> 01:02:21.137
to fall and get up again,

01:02:22.577 --> 01:02:24.338
to show that we are worthy of His

01:02:24.378 --> 01:02:28.382
attention and that we can be trusted to

01:02:28.402 --> 01:02:29.402
follow instructions.

01:02:31.423 --> 01:02:31.943
So indeed,

01:02:33.164 --> 01:02:35.465
there would eventually be those willing to

01:02:35.525 --> 01:02:37.807
listen and engage accordingly,

01:02:39.148 --> 01:02:43.451
and they would consume this fruit and

01:02:43.490 --> 01:02:44.251
become family.

01:02:48.396 --> 01:02:51.677
The initial exemplar of all of this was

01:02:51.757 --> 01:02:52.717
actually Noach,

01:02:53.577 --> 01:02:55.958
which is why he was lifted above the

01:02:56.018 --> 01:02:57.458
fallen, the Nephilim,

01:02:58.539 --> 01:03:00.601
the name means to fall,

01:03:01.181 --> 01:03:03.922
achieving this distinction by listening to

01:03:03.961 --> 01:03:07.282
Yahowah and then doing as God had asked,

01:03:08.282 --> 01:03:10.083
even caring for the animals that God

01:03:10.143 --> 01:03:12.485
enjoyed so much in the process.

01:03:13.893 --> 01:03:16.655
And this would serve as a sign of

01:03:16.695 --> 01:03:19.014
the Covenant made apparent by the seven

01:03:19.074 --> 01:03:21.376
colors of the rainbow as they broke

01:03:21.396 --> 01:03:23.056
through the stormy clouds.

01:03:23.076 --> 01:03:26.936
You can see that menorah with the seven

01:03:26.996 --> 01:03:29.117
colors of light of the rainbow spinning

01:03:30.077 --> 01:03:31.197
over my left shoulder.

01:03:35.478 --> 01:03:37.498
Even the eight souls above the ark,

01:03:37.518 --> 01:03:41.980
they were symbolic of the eight epochs

01:03:42.952 --> 01:03:44.733
of mankind's great adventure.

01:03:45.672 --> 01:03:48.153
It would take six millennia for enough of

01:03:48.233 --> 01:03:50.934
us to become interesting,

01:03:51.695 --> 01:03:54.355
to justify opening the Gan,

01:03:54.375 --> 01:03:56.195
this protective enclosure again.

01:03:57.056 --> 01:03:58.876
But the situation would be different this

01:03:58.916 --> 01:03:59.197
time,

01:03:59.876 --> 01:04:01.737
as the seventh millennium is our

01:04:01.777 --> 01:04:03.177
opportunity to get it right

01:04:04.137 --> 01:04:06.998
for the Tree of Knowledge and the eight

01:04:07.559 --> 01:04:09.799
individuals harvesting and sharing the

01:04:09.839 --> 01:04:10.640
fruit around him,

01:04:10.720 --> 01:04:13.601
those who were designated by the Shabuw'ah

01:04:13.641 --> 01:04:15.683
harvest and the Taruw'ah gleaning,

01:04:16.443 --> 01:04:18.643
and now acknowledged again on Sukah,

01:04:19.545 --> 01:04:22.385
to properly equip the mortal remnant of

01:04:22.425 --> 01:04:24.766
humanity for the greatest opportunity of

01:04:24.847 --> 01:04:24.987
all.

01:04:26.211 --> 01:04:28.293
And that is when beginning on the eighth

01:04:28.353 --> 01:04:30.032
day of Sukah shelters,

01:04:30.413 --> 01:04:32.393
those who have made a contribution,

01:04:32.733 --> 01:04:34.954
proven that they can be trusted and who

01:04:34.974 --> 01:04:36.994
have become interesting by learning,

01:04:37.594 --> 01:04:38.735
can be emancipated,

01:04:39.536 --> 01:04:42.096
free to explore the cosmos with our

01:04:42.135 --> 01:04:45.137
Creator in a fashion that is mutually

01:04:45.177 --> 01:04:48.217
beneficial because we're interesting,

01:04:48.498 --> 01:04:54.539
because we can be trusted at long last.

01:04:54.579 --> 01:04:55.340
Now, as a result,

01:04:56.416 --> 01:04:59.898
now you know why my collaboration with

01:04:59.958 --> 01:05:03.001
Yahowah would play out over thirty-two years

01:05:03.041 --> 01:05:05.902
from two thousand and one to twenty thirty-three

01:05:05.943 --> 01:05:06.262
three.

01:05:07.163 --> 01:05:11.065
And then eight years representing this

01:05:11.606 --> 01:05:14.668
transition through the eight days of Sukah

01:05:15.407 --> 01:05:16.809
and why it would require, well,

01:05:16.849 --> 01:05:17.648
so much effort,

01:05:17.668 --> 01:05:22.632
one hundred thousand hours already.

01:05:22.672 --> 01:05:23.253
Still counting,

01:05:24.273 --> 01:05:25.393
I would have to demonstrate

01:05:26.376 --> 01:05:29.117
the level of devotion required to prove

01:05:29.157 --> 01:05:31.619
that men could be trusted to work as

01:05:31.659 --> 01:05:35.161
intended, never giving up, falling,

01:05:35.842 --> 01:05:36.862
but standing again,

01:05:37.322 --> 01:05:38.844
making mistakes along the way,

01:05:39.224 --> 01:05:40.244
learning from them,

01:05:40.744 --> 01:05:41.365
growing as a result of them.

01:05:42.065 --> 01:05:44.746
Coming back to the same material,

01:05:45.126 --> 01:05:48.048
we have reviewed a score of times and

01:05:48.088 --> 01:05:50.369
then learning so much more from it at

01:05:50.389 --> 01:05:52.570
the right time that it's explosive

01:05:54.965 --> 01:05:57.228
in our understanding of who we are,

01:05:57.650 --> 01:05:58.329
where we are,

01:05:58.990 --> 01:06:00.853
and what we need to do to get

01:06:00.893 --> 01:06:05.119
from here to there.

01:06:05.139 --> 01:06:06.141
You know, in the process, sure,

01:06:06.161 --> 01:06:07.541
I'd be tripped up on occasion.

01:06:07.922 --> 01:06:08.943
I'd make some mistakes.

01:06:10.097 --> 01:06:12.719
All to show that I could dust myself

01:06:12.898 --> 01:06:13.079
off,

01:06:13.119 --> 01:06:15.440
correct the record and grow from there,

01:06:15.521 --> 01:06:16.561
build upon that.

01:06:17.222 --> 01:06:20.063
God wanted someone to affirm that by

01:06:20.143 --> 01:06:21.824
listening to Him and engaging accordingly,

01:06:22.065 --> 01:06:23.586
going to where His words lead,

01:06:23.606 --> 01:06:26.748
that we are capable of learning what would

01:06:26.768 --> 01:06:29.391
be required of us to be enriched and

01:06:29.451 --> 01:06:32.632
empowered and able and emancipated by Him

01:06:32.992 --> 01:06:35.255
to the extent that we become seven

01:06:35.295 --> 01:06:36.376
dimensional explorers.

01:06:39.795 --> 01:06:40.275
So yes,

01:06:41.416 --> 01:06:44.577
the Choter would have roots then and now.

01:06:45.436 --> 01:06:46.936
Branching out and bearing fruit,

01:06:47.898 --> 01:06:51.378
he would compose a sign that God speaks

01:06:51.438 --> 01:06:52.259
of as the nes,

01:06:53.739 --> 01:06:56.221
and he would have a voice thanks to

01:06:56.260 --> 01:06:57.340
the Spirit of this day.

01:06:59.661 --> 01:07:00.802
All the while,

01:07:00.862 --> 01:07:02.523
the partnership between the trees,

01:07:03.023 --> 01:07:05.724
the love and respect shared between the

01:07:05.824 --> 01:07:07.483
‘Ets Chayim and Da'ath,

01:07:08.125 --> 01:07:09.144
it's going to endure forever.

01:07:10.148 --> 01:07:11.668
Their branches intertwined.

01:07:13.309 --> 01:07:17.672
While Noach would point the way and ‘Abraham

01:07:17.713 --> 01:07:18.853
would be shown the way,

01:07:19.753 --> 01:07:22.956
while Mosheh would record the way and the

01:07:22.996 --> 01:07:24.476
prophets would explain the way,

01:07:25.958 --> 01:07:28.458
it would be the fruit of Dowd and

01:07:28.478 --> 01:07:32.442
Yada that would nourish those along the

01:07:32.461 --> 01:07:32.702
way.

01:07:38.184 --> 01:07:38.425
Yes.

01:07:39.625 --> 01:07:41.945
The fruit of these trees is the Covenant

01:07:41.965 --> 01:07:42.965
family.

01:07:43.786 --> 01:07:46.626
And Yahowah decides who has access to them

01:07:47.246 --> 01:07:50.007
and to it.

01:07:50.588 --> 01:07:52.128
So how do you like those apples?

01:07:54.949 --> 01:07:55.510
Collectively,

01:07:55.949 --> 01:07:58.210
what I've just shared with you is the

01:07:58.271 --> 01:08:01.311
pinnacle of human understanding pursuant

01:08:01.331 --> 01:08:01.711
to God.

01:08:02.632 --> 01:08:03.891
It's the reason for life.

01:08:04.692 --> 01:08:06.373
It is the essence of our existence.

01:08:08.001 --> 01:08:12.882
Do with this what you may.

01:08:12.902 --> 01:08:14.244
For reasons only God knows,

01:08:15.284 --> 01:08:16.664
I have been tasked with the

01:08:16.725 --> 01:08:17.604
responsibility,

01:08:17.765 --> 01:08:18.865
and I shouldn't actually say that,

01:08:18.905 --> 01:08:20.605
because God's actually made it quite clear

01:08:21.407 --> 01:08:22.447
as to what the reasons are.

01:08:23.627 --> 01:08:24.268
But nevertheless,

01:08:24.368 --> 01:08:26.229
I have been tasked with a responsibility I

01:08:26.309 --> 01:08:27.529
did not request,

01:08:28.710 --> 01:08:30.671
but I am not going to relinquish either,

01:08:33.671 --> 01:08:36.012
of reintroducing the world to Yahowah's

01:08:36.052 --> 01:08:36.273
name

01:08:37.891 --> 01:08:40.212
while simultaneously restoring His son's

01:08:40.252 --> 01:08:43.432
place in our lives.

01:08:43.573 --> 01:08:45.893
And while that's good, it's also bad.

01:08:47.253 --> 01:08:50.573
This job entails warning the world against

01:08:50.613 --> 01:08:52.354
the mess that men have made.

01:08:53.055 --> 01:08:53.875
By necessity,

01:08:53.975 --> 01:08:56.555
I must tell the world that Jesus is

01:08:56.635 --> 01:08:59.876
not God, that Allah is actually Satan,

01:09:00.815 --> 01:09:01.916
that there is no Hashem,

01:09:02.876 --> 01:09:05.096
that Marxists and MAGAs are both wrong,

01:09:05.957 --> 01:09:07.237
and that the current POTUS

01:09:08.795 --> 01:09:09.775
is actually demonic.

01:09:12.377 --> 01:09:15.578
The earth is spiraling out of control such

01:09:15.599 --> 01:09:18.541
that in the next eight years,

01:09:19.381 --> 01:09:21.021
catastrophe and disaster,

01:09:22.323 --> 01:09:24.444
destruction and death will be the

01:09:24.484 --> 01:09:25.944
hallmarks of this time.

01:09:27.246 --> 01:09:28.787
And standing up against it all,

01:09:29.567 --> 01:09:30.568
weathering the storm,

01:09:32.208 --> 01:09:33.309
is the deeply rooted,

01:09:33.750 --> 01:09:37.532
strong-branched Tree of Knowledge of good

01:09:37.572 --> 01:09:37.931
and bad.

01:09:41.515 --> 01:09:42.277
I'm doing my job.

01:09:43.438 --> 01:09:45.739
I'm producing fruit and I'm sharing it

01:09:45.779 --> 01:09:47.480
with all interested parties.

01:09:48.641 --> 01:09:51.444
Never has any man ever been as productive

01:09:51.864 --> 01:09:53.225
pursuant to the things of God.

01:09:54.606 --> 01:09:57.208
Nevertheless, my retirement is still,

01:09:57.989 --> 01:10:01.073
well, one millennium and eight years away.

01:10:02.793 --> 01:10:05.095
God doesn't shortchange anything now,

01:10:05.155 --> 01:10:05.496
does He?

01:10:05.976 --> 01:10:07.917
I've got another eight years here in this

01:10:07.978 --> 01:10:09.659
world as we know it

01:10:10.586 --> 01:10:13.328
and a thousand years in the garden to

01:10:13.828 --> 01:10:16.788
equip as many people as possible to

01:10:16.850 --> 01:10:19.591
explore the cosmos with Yahowah.

01:10:21.332 --> 01:10:24.734
So while it seems a bit anticlimactic,

01:10:24.814 --> 01:10:27.335
there is more to this story that God

01:10:27.375 --> 01:10:28.176
wants you to know.

01:10:29.796 --> 01:10:32.238
And so to rejoin His narrative where we

01:10:32.358 --> 01:10:32.957
left off,

01:10:33.479 --> 01:10:35.439
it is instructive to know that shama'

01:10:35.560 --> 01:10:38.501
| listening was cradled in the qowl

01:10:38.681 --> 01:10:39.242
| imperfect

01:10:40.324 --> 01:10:42.265
and the third person, masculine plural.

01:10:43.146 --> 01:10:43.587
Therefore,

01:10:43.627 --> 01:10:46.448
the implications are that the ones who are

01:10:47.448 --> 01:10:54.092
listening, who would listen to the ‘ets,

01:10:54.212 --> 01:10:56.474
the trees representing Dowd and Yada,

01:10:57.595 --> 01:10:59.215
are those of you who are listening now.

01:11:01.136 --> 01:11:05.019
‘Ets and they are masculine and the

01:11:05.099 --> 01:11:06.819
Yisra'elites and Gowym in the last

01:11:09.604 --> 01:11:11.306
days are also masculine,

01:11:12.368 --> 01:11:14.369
speaking of both groups of people.

01:11:15.570 --> 01:11:17.271
The result would play out over time

01:11:17.552 --> 01:11:19.154
because shama' was conveyed in the

01:11:19.194 --> 01:11:19.654
imperfect,

01:11:19.675 --> 01:11:22.898
and although nothing seemed to matter at

01:11:22.938 --> 01:11:24.179
the moment, it would,

01:11:24.899 --> 01:11:28.082
six thousand years thereafter.

01:11:28.103 --> 01:11:30.706
So having addressed the qowl of Yahowah,

01:11:31.600 --> 01:11:33.402
there is something more we can learn from

01:11:33.462 --> 01:11:34.002
halak.

01:11:34.582 --> 01:11:36.845
It was one of two successive verbs

01:11:36.925 --> 01:11:40.108
modified by the rare use of the hithpa'el

01:11:40.148 --> 01:11:40.488
stem.

01:11:41.149 --> 01:11:44.251
This means that both Yahowah and His qowl

01:11:44.270 --> 01:11:47.052
| voice, while regarded as one,

01:11:48.033 --> 01:11:50.195
are unaffected by the wiles of man.

01:11:50.216 --> 01:11:54.439
It was true of Yahowah having given up

01:11:54.498 --> 01:11:54.819
on ‘Adam.

01:11:55.805 --> 01:11:57.545
And it is true now of His voice

01:11:58.145 --> 01:12:02.546
being incongruous with the religious and

01:12:02.587 --> 01:12:05.307
the political.

01:12:05.347 --> 01:12:06.747
And in the participle form,

01:12:06.908 --> 01:12:10.868
God's movement through space and time is

01:12:10.929 --> 01:12:15.369
having a vividly depicted effect such that

01:12:15.430 --> 01:12:17.591
it leaves an indelible impression on our

01:12:17.631 --> 01:12:18.011
minds.

01:12:19.481 --> 01:12:22.404
This is particularly germane regarding the

01:12:22.524 --> 01:12:24.324
narrative which took place within the

01:12:24.385 --> 01:12:25.145
enclosed garden,

01:12:25.706 --> 01:12:28.186
which is why the Ruwach | Spirit is presented

01:12:28.226 --> 01:12:28.847
at this time.

01:12:29.488 --> 01:12:32.949
The fact is this was Yahowah's last time

01:12:33.810 --> 01:12:35.872
to move above the garden.

01:12:37.153 --> 01:12:40.534
And He will not return to travel above

01:12:40.574 --> 01:12:44.457
it again until a remnant of Yisra'el and

01:12:44.497 --> 01:12:47.479
some very fortunate Gowym are afforded

01:12:47.519 --> 01:12:48.380
that opportunity

01:12:49.507 --> 01:12:50.188
by the Choter,

01:12:51.448 --> 01:12:53.789
such that they can re-enter the garden and

01:12:54.831 --> 01:12:56.952
experience Yahowah's presence,

01:12:58.092 --> 01:13:00.793
particularly as it is represented through

01:13:00.833 --> 01:13:07.658
the ‘Elyown, who is His beloved Son, Dowd.

01:13:07.677 --> 01:13:08.637
Now, while it is subtle,

01:13:08.818 --> 01:13:11.118
there are a couple of reasons that Yahowah

01:13:11.420 --> 01:13:13.520
mentioned His Spirit in conjunction with

01:13:13.581 --> 01:13:13.961
listening.

01:13:15.164 --> 01:13:18.326
This pertains to His relative location in

01:13:18.386 --> 01:13:20.006
time and the nature of the garden

01:13:20.025 --> 01:13:21.105
yesterday and tomorrow.

01:13:21.886 --> 01:13:23.867
Without the seven Ruwach of Yahowah,

01:13:23.926 --> 01:13:26.247
the Choter would not have been able to

01:13:26.287 --> 01:13:28.927
discern what millions have missed over the

01:13:28.967 --> 01:13:29.408
millennia.

01:13:30.787 --> 01:13:33.088
And without being slandered by those

01:13:33.128 --> 01:13:36.189
falsely claiming that the Ruwach is a

01:13:36.288 --> 01:13:37.149
spirit mom,

01:13:38.050 --> 01:13:39.210
I would not have returned to this

01:13:39.270 --> 01:13:40.289
narrative at this time.

01:13:41.510 --> 01:13:41.930
Therefore,

01:13:42.449 --> 01:13:43.810
I would not have noticed the great

01:13:43.850 --> 01:13:44.810
discoveries that

01:13:46.430 --> 01:13:48.171
have resulted from this current

01:13:48.231 --> 01:13:51.574
investigation.

01:13:51.595 --> 01:13:53.756
This is why I have expressed and have

01:13:53.817 --> 01:13:56.878
recognized that Yahowah has noted with some

01:13:57.859 --> 01:13:59.881
extraordinary prophecies adroitly

01:13:59.921 --> 01:14:03.043
depicting what would be a fracture within

01:14:03.083 --> 01:14:07.766
the family, such that it serves a purpose,

01:14:08.287 --> 01:14:11.250
as did Chawah's flight of fancy and her

01:14:11.289 --> 01:14:12.350
rebellion on this day.

01:14:13.550 --> 01:14:17.300
We grow when we meet and rise above

01:14:18.342 --> 01:14:18.863
challenges.

01:14:18.944 --> 01:14:19.024
So.

01:14:23.034 --> 01:14:24.775
Moving even deeper into the preceding

01:14:24.796 --> 01:14:25.275
narrative.

01:14:25.796 --> 01:14:26.077
Well,

01:14:26.256 --> 01:14:28.899
the story depicts ‘Adam and Chawah together.

01:14:29.618 --> 01:14:32.400
It's the man who was shown as Chawah

01:14:32.520 --> 01:14:35.481
withdrawing from God because it was

01:14:35.521 --> 01:14:37.423
scribed in the third person masculine

01:14:37.463 --> 01:14:39.003
singular, as I mentioned previously.

01:14:39.265 --> 01:14:39.625
Further,

01:14:39.685 --> 01:14:41.865
since Chawah was modified by the hithpa'el

01:14:41.905 --> 01:14:42.246
stem,

01:14:42.747 --> 01:14:44.887
‘Adam is acknowledging that he is no longer

01:14:44.927 --> 01:14:47.448
being assisted by Chawah or influenced by

01:14:47.488 --> 00:14:47.789
God.

01:14:48.470 --> 01:14:50.792
This suggests that he, ‘Adam,

01:14:51.152 --> 01:14:54.094
decided to leave also on his own accord.

01:14:54.533 --> 01:14:58.317
So the parting was mutual between God and

01:14:58.356 --> 01:14:58.556
man.

01:14:58.577 --> 01:15:00.798
It didn't work out.

01:15:02.899 --> 01:15:04.841
All of this brings us right back to

01:15:04.881 --> 01:15:05.841
the ‘ets | tree,

01:15:06.122 --> 01:15:08.804
which remains masculine and singular

01:15:08.823 --> 01:15:09.283
throughout.

01:15:09.845 --> 01:15:11.945
This text does not say that ‘Adam was

01:15:11.985 --> 01:15:13.887
hiding among the trees, plural.

01:15:15.082 --> 01:15:16.823
He was ba tawak,

01:15:17.503 --> 01:15:19.966
in the midst of the one tree in

01:15:19.985 --> 01:15:21.605
the garden, in the Gan.

01:15:22.926 --> 01:15:24.268
It was the one he coveted,

01:15:24.728 --> 01:15:27.890
apparently trying to consume as much of it

01:15:27.930 --> 01:15:30.671
as he could prior to being escorted out

01:15:30.711 --> 01:15:31.291
of the garden.

01:15:32.072 --> 01:15:32.492
Therefore,

01:15:32.511 --> 01:15:34.672
while Chawah was the first to bite,

01:15:35.033 --> 01:15:36.554
wanting to be a mother goddess in her

01:15:36.594 --> 01:15:36.953
case,

01:15:38.015 --> 01:15:40.956
‘Adam was anything but an innocent

01:15:41.016 --> 01:15:41.716
bystander.

01:15:43.628 --> 01:15:46.210
So we're also reminded of what this ‘ets

01:15:46.270 --> 01:15:46.850
represents.

01:15:46.930 --> 01:15:49.631
The tree's purpose was to ‘etsah,

01:15:50.091 --> 01:15:52.391
provide counsel and advice through

01:15:52.431 --> 01:15:55.313
diligence and effort on the entirety of

01:15:55.353 --> 01:15:55.893
the plan,

01:15:56.514 --> 01:15:58.713
ultimately framing the issues that God

01:15:58.734 --> 01:15:59.515
wanted understood,

01:15:59.574 --> 01:16:02.496
providing the right perspective to advise

01:16:02.515 --> 01:16:03.456
people regarding them.

01:16:04.376 --> 01:16:06.136
And the process man would develop a

01:16:06.197 --> 01:16:08.358
backbone while overcoming challenges,

01:16:08.797 --> 01:16:11.939
all to advocate for the proper response.

01:16:13.618 --> 01:16:13.818
Sure,

01:16:13.837 --> 01:16:15.460
it would be painful at times as he

01:16:15.479 --> 01:16:18.243
would trip and fall to demonstrate the

01:16:18.302 --> 01:16:20.125
resolve to rise again,

01:16:21.827 --> 01:16:24.470
risking being shut out because his message

01:16:24.489 --> 01:16:26.431
would be an open defiance of the schemes

01:16:27.292 --> 01:16:30.136
proposed by those deemed authorized.

01:16:32.158 --> 01:16:33.560
I think that's a good place for us

01:16:33.600 --> 01:16:36.820
to stop this particular program.

01:16:37.301 --> 01:16:40.542
We'll rejoin in Yahowah's next statement,

01:16:40.561 --> 01:16:42.283
which is recorded in Bare'shiyth,

01:16:42.722 --> 01:16:45.123
Genesis 3:9.

01:16:45.845 --> 01:16:48.506
And it states that Yahowah, who is God,

01:16:48.565 --> 01:16:49.206
called out,

01:16:49.945 --> 01:16:52.367
issuing an invitation to read and recite

01:16:52.887 --> 01:16:53.427
| qara'.

01:16:54.380 --> 01:16:56.041
The verbal base of Miqra',

01:16:56.640 --> 01:16:58.783
the seven invitations for us to be called

01:16:58.882 --> 01:17:01.323
out of this world and to meet with

01:17:01.384 --> 01:17:01.724
God.

01:17:02.664 --> 01:17:05.947
And He's made this proclamation to the

01:17:05.987 --> 01:17:06.346
man.

01:17:07.386 --> 01:17:12.289
And He asked him, where are you?

01:17:12.369 --> 01:17:13.890
He's asking you the same question.

01:17:15.271 --> 01:17:16.131
Thank you for listening.

01:17:16.231 --> 01:17:17.073
We'll be back tomorrow.

